@*
    [TR] Bu dosya ne işe yarar: Sıkça Sorulan Sorular (SSS) sayfası.
    [TR] Neden gerekli: Kullanıcıların OCR, AI modelleri, dosya limitleri,
                        hesap ve gizlilik konularında en çok sorduğu soruları
                        tek bir sayfada Bootstrap accordion bileşeni ile sunar.
    [TR] İlgili: _Layout.cshtml üst menü "SSS" linki; HomeController.Faq().

    MODIFICATION NOTES (TR)
    - Yeni sorular eklemek için <div class="accordion-item"> bloğunu kopyalayıp
      heading/collapse id'lerini (faqN, collapseN) benzersiz yap.
    - İleride CMS tarzı yönetilsin istenirse controller'dan model olarak geçilebilir.
    - Zorluk: Kolay.
*@
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-9">

            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h1 class="h2 fw-bold mb-2">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                    Here are the most common questions about CreativeDoc.
                    If you cannot find what you need, you can contact us by email.
                </p>
            </div>

            @* [TR] ───── GENEL ───── *@
            <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3 mt-4">General</h2>
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush mb-4" id="faqGeneral">

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH1">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC1">
                            What is CreativeDoc?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC1" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH1" data-bs-parent="#faqGeneral">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            CreativeDoc is an <strong>ASP.NET Core MVC</strong> graduation project
                            that lets you extract text from selected PDF regions and run AI operations
                            such as translation, summarization, rewriting, creative writing, and visualization.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH2">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC2">
                            Is the system paid?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC2" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH2" data-bs-parent="#faqGeneral">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            The application itself is free. Some integrated AI providers
                            (for example, Google Gemini image generation models) may require a paid plan.
                            For free usage, you can choose <strong>Groq Llama</strong>,
                            <strong>HuggingFace Qwen</strong>, and <strong>FLUX.1 Schnell</strong> models.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            @* [TR] ───── PDF & OCR ───── *@
            <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3 mt-4">PDF &amp; OCR</h2>
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush mb-4" id="faqOcr">

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH3">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC3">
                            Which file types can I upload?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC3" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH3" data-bs-parent="#faqOcr">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            Currently, only <strong>PDF</strong> files are supported.
                            The maximum file size is <strong>20 MB</strong>.
                            Direct image uploads (JPG/PNG) are outside the current scope.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC4">
                            How does OCR work? Does it scan the whole document?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC4" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH4" data-bs-parent="#faqOcr">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            No. OCR only runs on the <strong>rectangular region selected by the user</strong>
                            on the document details page. This avoids unnecessary text processing and keeps the workflow faster.
                            <strong>Tesseract</strong> is used in the background, and PaddleOCR can be configured optionally.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH5">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC5">
                            Which languages does OCR support?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC5" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH5" data-bs-parent="#faqOcr">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            By default, <strong>Turkish</strong> and <strong>English</strong>
                            (<code>tur+eng</code>) language packs are available. The system detects the source language automatically.
                            The user only selects the <em>target translation language</em>.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            @* [TR] ───── AI MODELLERİ ───── *@
            <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3 mt-4">AI Models</h2>
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush mb-4" id="faqAi">

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH6">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC6">
                            Which AI providers are integrated?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC6" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH6" data-bs-parent="#faqAi">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            <ul class="mb-0 ps-3">
                                <li><strong>Google Gemini</strong> - text and image generation</li>
                                <li><strong>Groq</strong> - Llama 3.x and Qwen 3 (fast, free)</li>
                                <li><strong>HuggingFace</strong> — Qwen 2.5, FLUX.1 Schnell</li>
                                <li><strong>Stability AI</strong> - Stable Diffusion 3.5, Stable Image Core</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH7">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC7">
                            Which model is suitable for each task?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC7" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH7" data-bs-parent="#faqAi">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            <ul class="mb-0 ps-3">
                                <li><strong>Translation / Summarization / Rewrite / Creative Writing</strong> →
                                    Gemini 2.5, Llama 3.3 70B, Qwen 2.5</li>
                                <li><strong>Image Generation (Visualize)</strong> →
                                    Stable Diffusion 3.5, FLUX.1 Schnell, Gemini 3.1 Flash Image</li>
                            </ul>
                            The model list is filtered automatically according to the selected task.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH8">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC8">
                            I get an "invalid API key" error. What should I do?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC8" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH8" data-bs-parent="#faqAi">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            Paste the key from the relevant provider into
                            <code>Ai &gt; {Provider} &gt; ApiKey</code> in <code>appsettings.Development.json</code>.
                            For example, use <code>Ai:Gemini:ApiKey</code> for Gemini.
                            Requests are rejected if the key is empty or still a placeholder such as <code>YOUR_*_KEY</code>.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            @* [TR] ───── HESAP & GİZLİLİK ───── *@
            <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3 mt-4">Account &amp; Privacy</h2>
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush mb-4" id="faqAccount">

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH9">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC9">
                            Is email verification required during registration?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC9" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH9" data-bs-parent="#faqAccount">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            Yes. For security, you must click the verification link sent to your email address after registration.
                            You cannot log in until verification is complete.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH10">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC10">
                            I forgot my password. Can I reset it?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC10" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH10" data-bs-parent="#faqAccount">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            Yes. Use the <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="ForgotPassword">
                            <strong>Forgot Password</strong></a> link on the login screen and enter your email address.
                            A reset link will be created for you. Password rules: at least 8 characters,
                            one uppercase letter, one number, and one special character.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH11">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC11">
                            Are my documents and AI outputs stored?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC11" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH11" data-bs-parent="#faqAccount">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            Uploaded PDFs, OCR text, and AI results are stored in the local
                            <strong>SQLite</strong> database under your account.
                            You can view or delete them from the Notebook page at any time.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqH12">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqC12">
                            Is my data shared with third parties?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faqC12" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                         aria-labelledby="faqH12" data-bs-parent="#faqAccount">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                            During the selected AI operation, <em>only the relevant text or selected image</em>
                            is sent to the provider you choose (Gemini, Groq, HuggingFace, or Stability AI).
                            For more information, see the
                            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a> page.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            @* [TR] İletişim: Gmail web compose penceresini ön-dolu açar.
                    - "to"  : site iletişim adresi (appsettings.Email.Smtp.FromEmail)
                    - "su"  : konu başlığı
                    - "body": hazır metin şablonu
                    Kullanıcı başka mail istemcisi tercih ediyorsa mailto: linki
                    otomatik olarak devreye girer (noscript fallback).            *@
            <div class="text-center text-muted small mt-5">
                <p class="mb-2">Is your question not listed?</p>
                <a class="btn btn-accent btn-sm px-4"
                   href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=creativedocsystem@gmail.com&su=CreativeDoc%20Contact&body=Hello%20CreativeDoc%20team%2C%0D%0A%0D%0A"
                   target="_blank"
                   rel="noopener"
                   title="Send an email to creativedocsystem@gmail.com">
                    Contact us
                </a>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <a href="mailto:creativedocsystem@gmail.com?subject=CreativeDoc%20Contact"
                       class="link-secondary">
                        creativedocsystem@gmail.com
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
